decks.notes: The main strategy of this deck is to quickly cycle through cards and control the board until the player can cast Living End to bring back all creatures from both players' graveyards, essentially wiping the board and giving the player a significant advantage. The deck utilizes a combination of cycling creatures, disruption spells, and cascade effects to set up the Living End combo. The goal is to overwhelm the opponent with powerful creatures while maintaining control over the game through counter spells and card draw.
